column5: My kids got the chance to see him in his enclosure a few weeks ago
Does that mean winter is coming?
Wonder how many Willies they have gone through in my time ? Seem to remember an albino one at one time.
This was him. The one prior, when they went to get  him out for the predilection he was stiff!. The next one is called Wee Willie.
The next one is called Wee Willie.  Which is what men tend to have at the usual Feb temps!!
I think in 99 when the rodent died his name was Willie and next one was wee willie and it died and the next on was wee willie 2  lost track after that
